# scope|name|command|required|min_version|install_hint|notes
global|git|git|yes|2.30|Install Git.Git|Required for all repository operations and worktrees.
global|gh|gh|recommended|2.0|Install GitHub.cli|Used for PRs, repo creation, and GitHub automation.
global|python|python3|recommended|3.11|Install Python.Python.3.12|Needed for Python projects, notebooks, and local helpers.
global|node|node|recommended|20|Install OpenJS.NodeJS.LTS|Useful for web or JavaScript-based projects.
global|pandoc|pandoc|recommended|2.0|Install JohnMacFarlane.Pandoc|Required for DOCX export and document conversion.
global|latexmk|latexmk|recommended|4.0|Install MiKTeX.MiKTeX|Required for LaTeX builds in document-heavy projects.
global|copilot|copilot|optional|0.0|Install GitHub.CopilotCLI|Enable when using Copilot CLI as an agent.
python|langchain|pip install langchain langchain-community|recommended|0.1|Required for RAG orchestration.
python|chromadb|pip install chromadb|recommended|0.4|Vector database for local embeddings.
python|sentence-transformers|pip install sentence-transformers|recommended|2.0|Local embedding models.
python|pypdf|pip install pypdf|optional|4.0|Required for PDF reference indexing.
python|google-generativeai|pip install google-generativeai|recommended|0.4|For Gemini-based embeddings and generation.
